game.name: Dont Get Pinned
game.description:
A small square box is ready to go on a new adventure! However, obstacles available on its path do not let it go further. So it needs your help urgently. Do you think that you can guide it to the finish line? If yes, join Dont Get Pinned and be prepared to control a square and help it get the checkpoints. Make sure not to get your square pinned otherwise you would lose your game. Use your focus to deal with the complexities on this HTML5 physics-based platformer!
Your objective is to get to the finish while avoiding lava and other obstacles along the way. Keep your eyes on the little purple pinner that would try to stop you from moving forward! Do not let it pin you down otherwise you will lose. Try to reach out to the checkpoints where you can respawn at the last one you touched in this brand new adventure game! Keep your character away from the lava since it will kill you. 
This cool platform features 3 different modes and 105 unique and addictive levels to play through. Good luck to bounce your square to the finish while avoiding lava and pinners! Do not forget to check out other cool free adventure challenges for boys and girls on atmegame.com and allow yourself to enter the amazing world of thrill without download! We are pretty sure that it takes a few clicks to beat your boredom. All the best!
